    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-12-08T15:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-12-08T15:00:00-05:00" n="165"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d165">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">723.2515/349: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Shea</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-08T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 8, 1918, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You are directed to call upon the Minister for Foreign Affairs immediately and
                    inform him that the Minister for Foreign Affairs of Peru has asked the
                    Government of the United States if it had any objection to the publication of
                    the statement communicated to the Presidents of Chile and Peru by the United
                    States. That the Department has instructed the American Minister at Lima to
                    advise the Government of Peru that there was no objection on the part of the
                    Government of the United States to its publication and was so advising the
                    Government of Chile in order that that Government could take the same step if it
                    so desired.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
